Faculty/Research





      View Menu
      
Down arrow icon












Diverse, experienced faculty. Chicago's only public research university.
University of Illinois at Chicago is a tier 1 research university with world-renowned faculty solving real-world problems through the innovation and discovery that happens on campus.











